
Create method to define dungeon area
- Data structure set of cuboids
- Name the dungeon area
- Each subzone has a monster table
- Each subzone has list of available monster prefixes
- Each subzone also has a treasure table
- Subzone and monster treasure tables are added together.
- Dungeon Subzone enter messages
- Dungeon Zone enter and exit messages
- Monsters need to spawn regardless of lighting
- Outside monsters should not spawn or enter dungeon zones

Monsters
- Each monster is added to a list and associated with a prefix
- Prefix object allocated for every monster
- Prefix has a name, adds, multipliers and drops
- modify base health and damage

Treasure table data structure
- Each drop is calculated separately

Research can we modify properties of an item.
Save all data to disk.

